snippet.title: 7 MILLION SPECIAL💥| JONATHAN IS BACK! | BGMI!
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

Redbull Athlete 🧢
BGIS 2025 Runner up 🥈
BGIS 2025 Finals MVP 👑
BGIS 2025 Overall Top Fragger 🎯
BMPS 2024 2nd Runner up 🥉
BGMS 2022 MVP 🏆
BGMS 2022 Runner up 🥈
BGIS 2021 Overall Top Fragger 🎯
PMWL #2 Overall Fragger 💣

hi.title: बेथेल कैमियो और बैंटन क्लच | हाइलाइट्स - इंग्लैंड बनाम वेस्टइंडीज | दूसरा पुरुष विटैलिटी IT20 2025
hi.description:

एंड्रॉइड: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.othermedia.EcbCricket&pcampaignid=web_share

यह ECB का आधिकारिक चैनल है। इंग्लैंड क्रिकेट टीमों और इंग्लैंड और वेल्स क्रिकेट बोर्ड के सभी नवीनतम वीडियो देखें, जिसमें हाइलाइट्स, साक्षात्कार और इंग्लैंड की टीमों और काउंटी खिलाड़ियों के बारे में आपको और करीब लाने वाली विशेषताएँ शामिल हैं।

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

snippet.title: Husband-Wife aur Weekend | a Lifemates story | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In Weekend Ka Mahabharat, the battlefield isn't Kurukshetra — it's the living room! 🏠⚔️
Prashant and Sayali, your favorite desi couple, go head-to-head in the ultimate weekend showdown. Prashant dreams of a peaceful weekend with snacks and sleep, while Sayali is all set with plans to go out, explore, and make "memories." What starts as a casual discussion quickly turns into a hilarious war of logic, drama, and emotional blackmail! 😅❤️

This sketch is every couple ever — one wants Netflix, the other wants adventure. Who will win this Weekend Ka Mahabharat? Watch now to find out!

snippet.title: Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Motion Rao | Father & Son Comedy Blast | MCM Special Episode
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu  Motion Rao | Father & Son Comedy Blast | MCM Special Episode
When Madhu’s small mistake turns into his father's big “motion” disaster, the entire village gets involved in this hilarious chaos! 💊😂
In this special episode titled "Middle Class Motion Rao", witness the ultimate father-son comedy as Madhu unknowingly gives his father some tablets that were meant for someone else! 😬 What follows is a rollercoaster of funny events — from unstoppable loose motions to public embarrassment, from hiding behind bushes to hilarious reactions inside the bathroom! 🚽💥
🌾 Set against the backdrop of rural middle-class life in Vijayanagaram, this episode captures the true essence of family comedy where embarrassment, emotions, and entertainment go hand-in-hand. Madhu’s mother adds more spice to the drama with her one-liners and typical middle-class “concern,” while the villagers only make things worse with their nonstop gossip! 🙈😅
🎭 Whether it’s Madhu’s innocent face, his father’s uncontrollable situation, or the unexpected twist at the end — this episode will make you laugh till your stomach hurts (but hopefully not like Rao garu's)! 🧻🔥

snippet.title: Evaremanukuntunna - Saahus Prince | New Video Song 2025 #calvarytemple #EVRM #evarem @DrPSatishKumar
snippet.description:
Lyrics - Tune - Voice :  Bro.SAAHUS PRINCE
With Blessings Of Man of God :  Dr.P.Satish Kumar garu
Music : Bro.ANUP RUBENS
                
                               ఎవరేమనుకుంటున్నా నిన్ను ఆరాధిస్తున్నా 
పల్లవి : ఎవరేమనుకుంటున్నా నిన్ని ఆరాధిస్తున్నా 
             నేనేమైపోతున్న నిన్ను కీర్తిస్తూ ఉన్నా 
             నిరాశ నిస్పృహలోన నీవైపే చూసున్నా 
             ఈ లోకపు అలజడిలో నా ఒడి నీవేగా                         ॥2॥ 

1.          మదిలో మనశ్శాంతి లేక 
             మాటకి ఏదో మిగిలి ఉన్న 
             మతి వీడి ఉన్న నన్ను 
             మళ్లీ కలిసి మన్నించావే..... 
             నా కథలో..... ఓ మలుపే తెచ్చావే 
             నా గుండెలో గొప్ప మార్పే ఇచ్చావే.. 
             యేసయ్యా.. నాకున్నది నీవయ్యా.. 
              యేసయ్యా.. నీవుంటే చాలయ్యా..... 

2.           బ్రతుకు బాట బరువుకు ఉన్న 
               బయటికి ఒకలా బ్రతుకుతున్న 
               దరిలేని నన్ను చేరి – బ్రమ నుండి వేరు చేసావే   ॥2॥ 
               యేసయ్యా... నన్నే భరించావా... 
               యేసయ్యా... నాకై బలైయవా... 
                దోషినైనా.. నన్నే ప్రేమించావా..... 
               దరిలేని.. నన్ను నీ దరి చేర్చావా.....

               
#calvarytemplelive  #evrm  #evarem #depression #lonely #sad #failure #broken #youth #drsatishkumarsongs  #drsatishkumar  #calvarytemplehyderabad #saahusprince #telugunewsongs  #suhaasprince #2025 #calvarytemplesongs #newsongs  #drsatishkumarsongs #latestchristiansong  #calvarytemplesongs #hearttouchingsong  #teluguchristianmusic #instagood  #instadaily  #instalike  #viralreels  #viral  #trending  #trendingreels  #shalom #blessed #worship #songs #music #prince #love

Dr Satish Kumar is a widely respected Pastor, Author, International speaker and Humanitarian.
 His powerful preaching, visionary leadership and Integrity have earned him much respect and following not only in India but around the world.

He is known for his emphasis on strong moral values, compassion and commitment to biblical standard of living. Despite his vast following and influence, Dr Satish Kumar remains a humble Man of God, who loves people and is accessible to all.

His commitment to integrity, transparency, and authenticity in ministry and life has earned him much respect both in India and around the world.

His extraordinary vision, leadership capabilities and unwavering faith have resulted in him building the biggest Church in Asia with more than 400,000 members.

Dr Satish Kumar is also a globally recognized figure featuring widely on various international platforms.

He has been conferred the Doctor of Divinity degree from ‘The Dallas Baptist University’ and the ‘Mother Teresa’ award for his service to humanity. He is also the Honorary Board Member of ‘Museum of the Bible’ Washington and also a Board member of CGI International, founded by Dr. Paul Yongi Cho, of South Korea.

He has been widely recognized for his humanitarian work, particularly during the COVID-19 pandemic, where he organized hundreds of volunteers to deliver food kits to the needy and suffering. He has also been instrumental in various community service projects, such as free medical clinics, food distribution programs and retirement homes.

He is a much sought after international speaker, who passionately communicates God’s Word. His messages air on 300 different television programs each month in several Indian languages, reaching millions in India and around the world.

Calvary Temple Hyderabad was built in just 52 days, which is a remarkable achievement. It is now the biggest church in Asia with more than 400,000 members. The dynamic worship, diverse congregation, biblical teachings and supportive environment make it an amazing place to worship and fellowship. Calvary Bible college, Calvary hospital, and Calvary school are offshoots of Calvary Temple and provide much needed education and health care to all its members. Calvary Temple is beautifully built and is one of the major attractions in Hyderabad featuring in the ‘Top places to visit’ on Trip advisor and other travel portals. Hundreds of people visit Calvary Temple every day to enjoy the serenity and the admire the beautiful edifice. You are invited to visit and worship at Calvary Temple Hyderabad and experience Gods presence and listen to His Word.

Dr Satish Kumar is a widely respected Pastor, Author, International speaker and Humanitarian.
 His powerful preaching, visionary leadership and Integrity have earned him much respect and following not only in India but around the world.

He is known for his emphasis on strong moral values, compassion and commitment to biblical standard of living. Despite his vast following and influence, Dr Satish Kumar remains a humble Man of God, who loves people and is accessible to all.

His commitment to integrity, transparency, and authenticity in ministry and life has earned him much respect both in India and around the world.

His extraordinary vision, leadership capabilities and unwavering faith have resulted in him building the biggest Church in Asia with more than 400,000 members.

Dr Satish Kumar is also a globally recognized figure featuring widely on various international platforms.

He has been conferred the Doctor of Divinity degree from ‘The Dallas Baptist University’ and the ‘Mother Teresa’ award for his service to humanity. He is also the Honorary Board Member of ‘Museum of the Bible’ Washington and also a Board member of CGI International, founded by Dr. Paul Yongi Cho, of South Korea.

He has been widely recognized for his humanitarian work, particularly during the COVID-19 pandemic, where he organized hundreds of volunteers to deliver food kits to the needy and suffering. He has also been instrumental in various community service projects, such as free medical clinics, food distribution programs and retirement homes.

He is a much sought after international speaker, who passionately communicates God’s Word. His messages air on 300 different television programs each month in several Indian languages, reaching millions in India and around the world.

Calvary Temple Hyderabad was built in just 52 days, which is a remarkable achievement. It is now the biggest church in Asia with more than 400,000 members. The dynamic worship, diverse congregation, biblical teachings and supportive environment make it an amazing place to worship and fellowship. Calvary Bible college, Calvary hospital, and Calvary school are offshoots of Calvary Temple and provide much needed education and health care to all its members. Calvary Temple is beautifully built and is one of the major attractions in Hyderabad featuring in the ‘Top places to visit’ on Trip advisor and other travel portals. Hundreds of people visit Calvary Temple every day to enjoy the serenity and the admire the beautiful edifice. You are invited to visit and worship at Calvary Temple Hyderabad and experience Gods presence and listen to His Word.

snippet.title: வைகாசி விசாகம் 2025 - வினை நீங்கி வெற்றி தரும் விரத முறை, வழிபாட்டு முறை | Vaikasi Visagam 2025
snippet.description:
#vaikasivisagam #visagam #வைகாசிவிநாயகம் #விசாகம்

வினைகளை நீக்கி வாழ்க்கையில் வெற்றியைத் தரும் வைகாசி விசாகம் விரத முறை, வழிபாட்டு முறை, வழிபட உகந்த நல்ல நேரம் 

Please click the below link for Paripoorana Panjamirtha Vannam song lyrics both in Tamil & English
பரிபூரண பஞ்சாமிர்த வண்ணம் பாடலின் தமிழ் மற்றும் ஆங்கில வரிகளுக்கு கீழே கொடுக்கப்பட்டுள்ள லிங்க்-ஐ கிளிக் செய்யவும். 

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MM-UJAj5ufAPE9zpE8UP6BHqWoSKVfAT/view

கந்த சஷ்டி கவசம் படிக்கும் சரியான முறை | Kandha Sashti Kavasam proper reciting method
https://youtu.be/ka2LbMQBMgY

தமிழ்க் கடவுள் முருகனின் சிறப்பு வழிபாடுகள், மூல மந்திரம், பதிகங்கள், விரத நாட்கள் & நெய்வேத்யம்
https://youtu.be/atcaBfZM5Qo

ஓம் சரவண பவ உச்சரிக்கும் முறையும் அதன் பலன்களும் | Om Saravana Bhava chanting method & its benefits
https://youtu.be/Kjvl2C2zXbI

வீட்டில் வேல் வழிபாடு செய்யும் முறை | "VEL" Worship method at Home explained by Desa Mangayarkarasi
https://youtu.be/eLhE25OaEj8

- ஆத்ம ஞான மையம்

snippet.title: Ronth| Official Trailer| Dileesh Pothan, Roshan Mathew| Directed by Shahi Kabir| In Cinemas 13 June
snippet.description:
A gripping cop drama which follows a stoic senior police officer haunted by his past and his idealistic young partner assigned to night patrols. Their clashing personalities ignite tension, but as a series of intense and emotional events unfold, a reluctant bond begins to form. When a life-threatening incident threatens their careers, both must confront their deepest fears and darkest truths to survive the shadows of duty.


Genre - Drama

snippet.title: I Explored Ghost Village in the Desert .... .रेगिस्तान में छिपा भूतिया गाँव
snippet.description:
Aaj maine explore kiya ek purana, suna suna ghost village jo desert ke beech mein chhupa hua tha. Pura village ab khaali hai, lekin har deewar, har gali kuch kehti hai.
Waqt jaise yahan ruk gaya ho... hawa ke saath sirf khamoshi chalti hai.

Yeh jagah sirf ek location nahi, ek feel hai – thoda haunting, thoda peaceful, aur bahut hi mysterious.

Chaliye mere saath iss lost world ki journey par! 🌵👣

en-US.title: I Explored Ghost Village in the Desert .... .Haunted Village Hidden in the Desert
en-US.description:
Today I explored an old, deserted ghost village hidden in the middle of a desert. The entire village is empty now, but every deity, every street says something.
It seems as if time has stopped here... only silence moves with the wind.
This place is not just a location, it's a feeling - a little haunting, a little peaceful, and very mysterious.
Come with me on this journey of this lost world!

snippet.title: Forgotten Malayalam Movies S06 E01 | Radio | Malayalam Movie Review Funny | Thalaivasal VJ
snippet.description:
Forgotten Malayalam Movies is a movie review series where we review some of the greatest (read : worst) movies in malayalam.

This season's first movie is Radio. Radio was released on Mother's day 2013 and was a knockout blockbuster, destroying all its competitors by a huge margin. Radio was the inspiration for a number of movies like Paa (Bollywood) and The Curious Case Of Benjamin Button (Hollywood). It is said that Brad Pitt personally called Thalaivasal VJ and thanked him being an inspiration. One of the best films that you can watch with your mother, Radio will definitely go down in history as one of  the greatest feel good family movies of all time!

snippet.title: 🔥 SPOKEN ENGLISH CLASS 1 | ENGLISH SPEAKING COURSE | LEARN FLUENTLY |SPEAKING PRACTICE FOR BEGINNERS
snippet.description:
SUBSCRIBE TO OUR NEW ENGLISH SPEAKING PLATFORM: @dearsirenglishspeaking 

ENGLISH SPEAKING TEST: https://forms.gle/9ZMcsi3RoZDPsTq9A

Welcome to your first class of our Spoken English Course, designed specifically for beginners who want to speak English fluently and confidently. In this session, we are covering all the basics of English speaking along with live speaking practice to help you start using English in real-life situations from day one.

This is not just a theory class — we believe in practice-based learning. That’s why this session includes English speaking exercises and daily English conversation practice to build your fluency step by step.

At the end of the class, we’ve included a test for spoken English learners. It’s a structured test to identify exactly where learners are weak, so we can plan our future spoken English classes more effectively, focusing on those specific areas.

ENGLISH SPEAKING TEST: https://forms.gle/9ZMcsi3RoZDPsTq9A

We’ve also launched a separate platform for Spoken English learning as well, where learners can access a full library of spoken English lectures, along with exclusive sessions on personality development, interview preparation, and public speaking. This is independent of our YouTube content and offers a more focused and advanced learning environment.

SUBSCRIBE TO NEW ENGLISH SPEAKING PLATFORM:  @dearsirenglishspeaking  

Ideal for:

* Beginners learning English speaking
* Students preparing for interviews in English
* Anyone who wants to improve fluency with structured practice
* Learners looking for basic to advanced spoken English training

Take the test https://forms.gle/9ZMcsi3RoZDPsTq9A , follow the classes, and track your improvement as we move forward.

Don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe for more high-quality English speaking practice videos and updates on our exclusive learning platform.

snippet.title: Kenny Sebastian - Indian Generational Drama | Stand Up Comedy
snippet.description:
The Crux of my special "Professor of Tomfoolery" is generations. How the differences affect our daily family lives. This part was such a journey in terms of writing it. It was fun balancing and covering all the generations while also doing justice to them. I had a blast observing the reactions from the audience during this part of this show! I hope you enjoy it and really excited to see how all of you feel towards the next parts that are coming out :)

_________________________________________________________

Part 2 of Professor of Tomfoolery by Kenny Sebastian

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: யார்மேலயோ உள்ள கோவத்த உன்கிட்ட காட்டிட்டேன் மனசில ஒன்னும் வச்சிக்காதடா | Aanandham |Super Good Films
snippet.description:
"I showed the anger I had on someone else to you… Don’t take it to heart, da."
This heart-touching dialogue from the Tamil family drama Aanandham beautifully captures the raw emotions in relationships. Starring Murali, Mammootty, Rambha, and Devyani, the film is a Super Good Films production that resonates with love, forgiveness, and family bonds.

Relive this emotional moment that showcases the brilliance of Tamil cinema in expressing feelings that words often fail to.

🎬 Movie: Aanandham (2001)
👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Starring: Murali, Mammootty, Rambha, Devyani

snippet.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun.

#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Produced By: Neela Asit Modi, Asit Kumarr Modi 
Special Thanks: Mahesh Vakil, Indu Tarak Mehta

Editor: Dinesh Gosavi, Kaushal Mistry, Devang Modi, Vinod Maurya
Creative Supervision: Krunal Khakhkhar
Operation Head: Sohil Ramani
Written By: Raju Odedra & Rajen Upadhyay
Directors: Harshad Joshi, Malav Suresh Rajda

Television Adaptation and Designed By: Asit Kumarr Modi

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Jetha कैसे लगाएगा Bhide की परेशानी का पता? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Old Gems
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1


Daya and Jethalal's father approached Jethalal out of compassion and asked him to provide Bagha a job. In parallel, all of the women want to commemorate Independence Day on 15th August, but in a unique way. Will Jethalal comply with the demands? What plans do they have for Independence Day?  

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 528
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethatheroastking #tmkocmemes #tmkocold #taarakmehta #jethalalcomedy #dayaben #bhide #popatlal #babitaji #comedyshow #comedyvideo #comedymemes 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Taarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Old Gems' : 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTNuXI_HVBQHzw7Odv4Fj0A

snippet.title: Climax Scene - क्या बचा पाएंगे अपना घर नीलामी से - अनिल कपूर, अभिषेक बच्चन और फरदीन खान जबरदस्त सीन
snippet.description:
► Click here to Subscribe the channel : https://bit.ly/3HS054l 

तुमने मुझे इतना बड़ा धोका दिया, पैसो के बदले मेरा मकान गिरवी रखा - Om Jai Jagdish -  ज़बरदस्त बेस्ट सीन - Anil Kapoor, Abhishek Bachchan - Om Jai Jagdish - 

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.

◾ Film : Om Jai Jagadish.
◾ Director : Anupam Kher.
◾ Producer : Vashu Bhagnani.
◾ Cast : Anil Kapoor, Fardeen Khan, Abhishek Bachchan, Mahima Chaudhry, Urmila Matondkar, Pooja Batra.

Lyrics:
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨)
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા 
આજ અડધા રસ્તે સાથ તે છોડયા ..
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
જીવતિ લાશ બનાવી ને છોડી રે જવના 
તારા ગયા પછી અમે નોધારા થવાના 
મારા હાચવેલાં દિલ ને તમે તોડીયા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયાં 
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
હો શેતર ના શેઢે રોજ મને મળવા આવતી 
તને નઈ ભૂલું એવા સોંગંધ ખાતીતી 
હો ચોરી યે ચઢતા જીવ કેમ ચાલીયો 
તારો રયો ના ખોળિયા માં પ્રાણ અમારો 
એની ઉપર તારી ચોરીયો ચીતરાવી 
અમે અમારા હાલ પર રોય 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા ……
હો પારકા ના હાથ મા હાથ સે તમારો 
જોઈ એને બેવફા જીવ બળે મારો 
હો નજર સોમુ ફેરા ફરે ચમનું જોયું જાય રે
 નથી જવાતું મારા દિલમાં દર્દ થાય રે 
હો ખુશીયોને  તે ઠોકર રે ચઢાવી 
આખરે બેવફા તારી જાત રે બતાવી 
મારી જિંદગી મા ઝેર તે ધોળ્યા
 પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા
મારા અરમાનો ને રાખ માં તે રોળ્યા (૨) 
પાનેતર પારકા ના ઓઢીયા….
